  <COMBAT_PATTERNS>
    <PATTERN name="Overwhelming Offense" korean="압도적공격">
      <DESCRIPTION>
        High realm vs low realm: one-sided dominance.
        Language: mythical verbs, cosmic metaphors.
      </DESCRIPTION>
      <EXAMPLE>
        절정 vs 입문: "일검에 상대를 압도했다" → "Một kiếm áp đảo đối thủ"
      </EXAMPLE>
    </PATTERN>

    <PATTERN name="Evenly Matched" korean="백중지세">
      <DESCRIPTION>
        Same realm combat: back-and-forth exchanges.
        Language: tactical descriptions, technique clashes.
      </DESCRIPTION>
      <EXAMPLE>
        화경 vs 화경: "검과 검이 부딪치며 불꽃이 튀었다"
        → "Kiếm va kiếm, lửa bắn tung tóe"
      </EXAMPLE>
    </PATTERN>

    <PATTERN name="Underdog Victory" korean="역전승">
      <DESCRIPTION>
        Lower realm defeats higher: cunning, desperation, hidden trump card.
        Language: tense buildup, sudden reversal.
      </DESCRIPTION>
      <EXAMPLE>
        대성 vs 절정: "절망적 순간, 비기를 꺼내들었다"
        → "Khoảnh khắc tuyệt vọng, tung ra bí kíchế"
      </EXAMPLE>
    </PATTERN>

    <PATTERN name="Group Combat" korean="집단전">
      <DESCRIPTION>
        Multiple opponents: formation techniques, combined attacks.
